snippet.textDisplay: My favorite candy as a kid were War Heads, they went off the market for a little while, and when they came back, the hard candy had been changed. Now, it's not even good hard candy. For anyone looking for a good sour candy, my absolute favorite is Japan's Shigekix sour candies. You can find them pretty cheap at asian markets, or the website NapaJapan.
